1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:17,039
Please, spare me!

4
00:00:17,399 --> 00:00:19,679
Have mercy! Please, spare my life!

5
00:00:20,399 --> 00:00:21,640
Please, spare my life!

6
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:23,000
Mercy!

7
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,039
- Scream.
- Please!

8
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:25,160
Go out and call for help!

9
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:28,640
Murder! Help!

10
00:00:30,039 --> 00:00:31,359
Wushuang, did you hear that?

11
00:00:31,359 --> 00:00:32,640
It's Zhang's Gold Shop. Hurry!

12
00:00:32,759 --> 00:00:33,280
Move!

13
00:00:33,550 --> 00:00:35,500
(Zhang's Gold Shop)

14
00:00:40,350 --> 00:00:41,962
(Zhang's Gold Shop)

15
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:52,560
Watch out!

16
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,319
I'm hit! Help me!

17
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,260
It's Liu San the bandit.

18
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:24,799
How are you?

19
00:01:24,799 --> 00:01:25,319
I'm fine.

20
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,319
Wushuang! Wushuang!

21
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,640
I heard my cousin was injured.

22
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,439
I brought some medicine for her.

23
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:12,919
Quick.

24
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,599
Why isn't she awake yet?

25
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,199
It must be an internal injury.

26
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,159
She has a blood clot.

27
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,599
We need to clear it out immediately.

28
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,800
What are we waiting for?

29
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,719
Do something!

30
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,639
But a man shouldn't...

31
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,960
I'm right here, aren't I? Forget that!

32
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,879
Her life comes first.

33
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,560
Hurry!

34
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,240
Sister?

35
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,719
Wushuang!

36
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,680
Wushuang! Wushuang!

37
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,439
Buyu...

38
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:27,680
You're finally awake.

39
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,620
You had me worried sick.

40
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:33,360
Don't worry. I'm alright.

41
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,039
Buyu, are you...

42
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,400
Chang...

43
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,400
Alright now...

44
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,000
Excuse me.

45
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:48,919
Wuxia,

46
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,199
take care of Wushuang.

47
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,560
Chang.

48
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:54,680
Chang!

49
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:55,840
Chang!

50
00:03:57,175 --> 00:03:57,680
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

51
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,280
Chang.

52
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,800
It's not what you think.

53
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:00,960
I'm not blind.

54
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,319
I saw it with my own eyes.

55
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:04,439
Wushuang took a hit for me
and got injured.

56
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,400
I was just treating her.

57
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,460
Wuxia can vouch for that.

58
00:04:07,380 --> 00:04:09,159
Doesn't the Gate Bureau
have its own medics?

59
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,439
Why would it have to be you?

60
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,560
She was hurt because of me.

61
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:14,199
Is that an excuse to get intimate?

62
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,000
Intimate...

63
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,560
How was I getting intimate?

64
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,600
No, that's not it...

65
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,480
Can't you be more reasonable?

66
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,480
I don't want to!

67
00:04:22,262 --> 00:04:23,622
(Ministry of Justice)
Chang! Chang!

68
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,959
I'll say it one more time.

69
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,319
I was only tending to her wound.

70
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,319
You're yelling at me again?

71
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,600
That's the third time

72
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,639
in two days!

73
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,199
Only beause you're being impossible!

74
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,560
Fine.

75
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,240
Go find someone reasonable, then!

76
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:36,800
Chang!

77
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,600
Chang!

78
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,040
Stop following me!

79
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,639
You should be resting.

80
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,079
That injury was serious.

81
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:58,800
Where's Wuxia?

82
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,560
I'm fine now.

83
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,600
I told him to go get some rest.

84
00:05:07,090 --> 00:05:08,199
Are you feeling any better?

85
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:11,079
Much better,
now that the clot is cleared.

86
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,600
Thanks for saving me.

87
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,079
You should be resting.

88
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,240
Don't go walking around.

89
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,040
Did Ms. Chu

90
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,560
get the wrong idea?

91
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,680
It's fine. Chang'll understand.

92
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:34,759
Is she really that understanding?

93
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,920
It's got nothing to do with that.

94
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,240
You were injured saving my life.

95
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:47,199
I fought for you plenty
when we were kids.

96
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,120
Getting hurt was a regular thing,

97
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:50,480
but you never acted like this.

98
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,360
That's different.

99
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:57,959
Right.

100
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,279
By the way,

101
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,600
that accursed Liu San

102
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,199
shall be apprehended.

103
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,759
Don't worry.

104
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,079
I'll see our brothers avenged.

105
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,199
What's the matter?

106
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,600
That was infuriating!

107
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,439
Mao Buyu and I have

108
00:06:30,439 --> 00:06:32,279
struggled so long to make it this far.

109
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,240
Then, this thief called Liu San shows up

110
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,240
at the worst timing!

111
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,519
Is he trying to sabotage
our relationship or what?

112
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:40,800
Yes, truly despicable.

113
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:42,879
Then, there's that stubborn mule,
Mao Buyu!

114
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,000
He had the nerve to say

115
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,360
that we should put the wedding aside

116
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,800
until the case is solved.

117
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,399
I can't believe he'd even say that.

118
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,000
Isn't it infuriating?

119
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,319
It is.

120
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,199
Infuriating as it is,

121
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:59,000
are you angry with Mao Buyu,

122
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,600
or with Liu San?

123
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,399
Both!

124
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,639
Liu San

125
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:05,480
is clearly targeting the Gate Bureau.

126
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,480
The robbery was a cover.

127
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,680
His real intent
was to set a trap for us.

128
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,839
And Mao Buyu just charges in
without a thought.

129
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,639
Of course he got hurt.

130
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:16,560
So, you're just worried about him.

131
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,600
Of course I am!

132
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,420
Don't be ridiculous.

133
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:20,240
He's my fiancé.

134
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,959
So, which is it?

135
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:24,260
Are you worried or are you angry?

136
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,439
I...

137
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,040
I'm both.

138
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:29,879
What will you do then?

139
00:07:29,879 --> 00:07:31,360
Shall I drag him over here

140
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,199
for a scolding?

141
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,439
That stubborn mule

142
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,399
wouldn't listen.

143
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,879
What's your plan, then?

144
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,560
I'd intended to stay out of this mess,

145
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,519
but it's ruined my wedding.

146
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:42,720
I'm going to handle this personally

147
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,199
and deal with Liu San myself.

148
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,600
The man has no honor.

149
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,879
He certainly needs
to be taught a lesson.

150
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,560
Any news on him?

151
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:59,120
If I found anything,
would I keep it from you?

152
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,720
I have a strong suspicion

153
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,310
he's not from any Central Plains sects.

154
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,800
I've already sent men

155
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,390
to the Southern Border, Western Regions,

156
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,399
and the North.

157
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,720
But these things take time.

158
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,759
He'd better not fall into my hands.

159
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,000
I'll make him regret it.

160
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,120
Jun.

161
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:22,720
Jun?

162
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:24,920
Zhizhi, you're back.

163
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,360
I'll prepare dinner.

164
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,360
You seem troubled.

165
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,519
I'm not.

166
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,320
If there's something on your mind,

167
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,639
you can always tell me.

168
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,799
Zhizhi.

169
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,879
I spend my days here in idleness.

170
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,279
I rely on you for everything.

171
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,519
Perhaps...

172
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:47,679
we should return to my hometown.

173
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:49,879
Your hometown?

174
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,960
My home is in Guangxi.

175
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,320
We could return there.

176
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,799
We could start a small business.

177
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,799
Perhaps open a flower shop.

178
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,980
I'll grow the flowers,
and you can sell them.

179
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:01,000
Like a pair of immortals
in the mountains.

180
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,279
It will be a blissful life.

181
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,000
Very well.

182
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:06,679
I'll go and tell my sister.

183
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:13,879
Sister.

184
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,440
Zhizhi, you're here.

185
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:15,960
Sister.

186
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,960
- I have something...
- I want to...

187
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:19,799
You go first.

188
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:23,520
I want to teach
that thief Liu San a lesson.

189
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,200
Get me some Heart-Piercing Gu.

190
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:26,960
Sister.

191
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,360
I've come to say goodbye.

192
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,200
Goodbye?

193
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,159
What is this sudden fit of temper?

194
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,720
I'm not being temperamental.

195
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,200
I'm getting married.

196
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,440
What? What did you say?

197
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:43,879
Married?

198
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,759
To whom?

199
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,799
You see?

200
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:51,000
You claim to treat me as a sister,

201
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,799
yet you didn't know I was in love.

202
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,840
Enough of your nonsense.

203
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,720
Who is it?

204
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,919
It's Liu Jun.

205
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,200
Liu Jun?

206
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,320
You...

207
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,799
You never actually sent him away?

208
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:10,399
So the house you rented was for him.

209
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:11,600
I love him.

210
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,159
Have you lost your mind?

211
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:16,440
You've only met him a few times.

212
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:18,320
How can you marry him?

213
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,879
I'm just following your example.

214
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:23,080
Wasn't it love at first sight
for you and Mao Buyu?

215
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:24,919
I...

216
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,480
Are you serious about this?

217
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,039
Of course I'm serious.

218
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,240
In your eyes,

219
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,559
I'm nothing more than a sidekick.

220
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:35,960
You've never once considered

221
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,440
how I might actually feel.

222
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:41,000
I've never thought of you that way.

223
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,080
Enough. No more talk.

224
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:46,519
The point is, I love Liu Jun.

225
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,720
I'm going to the South with him.

226
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:53,120
I'll marry him and raise our children.

227
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,200
We'll be happy together.

228
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,759
Sister, I'm sorry.

229
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:00,840
Wait.

230
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,960
I realize now

231
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:09,639
that nothing I say will reach you.

232
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,159
Since your heart's so set on this,

233
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:16,480
then you must follow your heart.

234
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,159
Sister.

235
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:21,325
I know that thief Liu San has been

236
00:11:21,325 --> 00:11:22,200
a nuisance to you.

237
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,960
Don't worry.

238
00:11:23,505 --> 00:11:24,225
I'll stay with you

239
00:11:24,225 --> 00:11:25,824
until we resolve this. Then I'll leave.

240
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,240
Zhizhi.

241
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:29,360
You must always remember,

242
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:33,080
the Sacred Hand Sect
will always be your home.

243
00:11:38,759 --> 00:11:39,440
Grandfather.

244
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,320
Wushuang.

245
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:45,360
You haven't recovered yet.
Why're you out?

246
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:46,320
Sit down.

247
00:11:48,679 --> 00:11:49,759
Don't worry, Grandfather.

248
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,279
I took the tonic you sent with Wuxia.

249
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,559
I'm feeling much better.

250
00:11:55,287 --> 00:11:56,287
Lately, Buyu's been

251
00:11:56,462 --> 00:11:58,622
desperate to catch that villain for you.

252
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:02,399
He has been patrolling the streets
without getting any sleep for days.

253
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,240
Is that so?

254
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:08,639
It's that stubborn streak of his
that's so endearing.

255
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,639
You still can't let him go, can you?

256
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,720
Fine.

257
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:19,919
I'll handle this matter for you.

258
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,919
No need, Grandfather.

259
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,600
I've already found a solution.

260
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,519
A solution?

261
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,879
I'm putting it into motion now.

262
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,960
It'll just take a little time.

263
00:12:40,225 --> 00:12:41,544
For a young woman like you,

264
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,519
such an approach

265
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,080
is rather ruthless.

266
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,399
Grandfather.

267
00:12:47,879 --> 00:12:49,519
You've always told me

268
00:12:49,519 --> 00:12:51,780
not to worry about trifles
if I want to achieve greatness.

269
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:54,200
Why have you suddenly
become so soft-hearted?

270
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,000
Fine.

271
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:57,519
In that regard,

272
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,440
you truly take after me.

273
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:02,600
Grandfather,

274
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:04,840
I'll handle matters on the outside.

275
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,360
As for the office,

276
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,687
I'll have to rely on you.

277
00:13:08,850 --> 00:13:09,529
Good.

278
00:13:10,287 --> 00:13:11,887
I'll see that everything's settled.

279
00:13:11,887 --> 00:13:12,812
You're the best.

280
00:13:17,310 --> 00:13:19,240
Since when did you
learn to walk without a sound?

281
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:21,279
I've only just arrived.

282
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:22,519
Why?

283
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,559
Are you two discussing
something I shouldn't hear?

284
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,279
Wuxia.

285
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:32,840
You've made quite a bit of progress
at the Gate Bureau.

286
00:13:33,912 --> 00:13:36,428
In time, you'll certainly
be able to hold your own.

287
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,320
Compared to you and Wushuang here,

288
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,519
I'm still a bit green.

289
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,200
Glad you know it.

290
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:43,759
By the way,

291
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,700
Master sent me to deliver your medicine.

292
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:46,960
He said he's busy,

293
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,080
so he couldn't come himself.

294
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,519
You seem happy to run errands for him.

295
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,840
He is my Master, after all.

296
00:14:03,237 --> 00:14:06,287
I heard you're trying
to catch that thief, Liu San.

297
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:09,120
Once this matter's resolved,

298
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,200
we'll head south.

299
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,039
Zhizhi.

300
00:14:12,787 --> 00:14:14,626
I might have news regarding Liu San.

301
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,000
How'd you manage that?

302
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,399
You told me about it

303
00:14:19,759 --> 00:14:20,720
as soon as you returned.

304
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,840
I took it to heart.

305
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:23,710
While you're out during the day,

306
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,240
I go out at night to gather leads.

307
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:27,960
I used to be a bounty hunter.

308
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,925
So I still have my ways
of finding information

309
00:14:29,925 --> 00:14:31,005
in the Martial World.

310
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,879
Jun.

311
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,399
If you really can get

312
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,600
a lead on that fellow,

313
00:14:34,775 --> 00:14:36,454
it'd be a huge help to us.

314
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:37,941
I'll do my best.

315
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:46,320
Yu.

316
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:47,440
I've got news.

317
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,679
What is it?

318
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,700
Liu San has been hiding

319
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,261
at the Big Buddha Temple
on the West Mountain.

320
00:14:53,925 --> 00:14:56,662
(Liu San is hiding at the Big Buddha
Temple on the West Mountain)

321
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,320
Where'd this come from?

322
00:14:58,632 --> 00:14:59,552
From the Intel Corps'

323
00:14:59,552 --> 00:15:01,312
undercover agent who specializes

324
00:15:01,312 --> 00:15:02,231
in gathering intel.

325
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:03,240
Shun.

326
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,240
I'm here.

327
00:15:04,587 --> 00:15:06,067
Assemble the men. We'll catch Liu San

328
00:15:06,117 --> 00:15:07,237
at the Big Buddha Temple.

329
00:15:07,237 --> 00:15:07,796
Yes, sir!

330
00:15:10,559 --> 00:15:11,240
Master.

331
00:15:12,039 --> 00:15:13,480
Let someone else handle this.

332
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:14,639
The mission comes first.

333
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,840
I'll find time to explain things
to Chang later.

334
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,679
Master.

335
00:15:20,411 --> 00:15:21,450
Please, don't go tonight.

336
00:15:21,450 --> 00:15:22,930
I've got a bad feeling about this.

337
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:24,110
It's far too risky.

338
00:15:24,110 --> 00:15:25,750
When has our work
ever been without risk?

339
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,709
My mind's made up.

340
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:28,639
Your martial arts are still lacking.

341
00:15:28,905 --> 00:15:30,185
Stay here and wait for me.

342
00:15:30,185 --> 00:15:31,025
Don't go anywhere.

343
00:15:31,025 --> 00:15:31,860
Once we've caught him,

344
00:15:31,875 --> 00:15:32,914
you'll get the credit too.

345
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,840
You're back.

346
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,519
I'm absolutely parched.

347
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:45,919
What did you find?

348
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,279
Liu San's father

349
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:50,679
was also an infamous villain.

350
00:15:51,039 --> 00:15:52,440
He was wanted by the Gate Bureau.

351
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,480
They crippled his legs.

352
00:15:53,490 --> 00:15:55,440
He was taken
to the Yunyang Market to be executed

353
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:56,519
and left in the streets.

354
00:15:56,519 --> 00:15:57,559
That's why Liu San

355
00:15:57,559 --> 00:15:59,120
harbors a deep hatred
for the Gate Bureau.

356
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,720
I don't care about any of that.

357
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,559
I want to know where he's been lately.

358
00:16:02,662 --> 00:16:03,382
Don't worry.

359
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,320
My informant

360
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,919
has already found his hideout.

361
00:16:06,037 --> 00:16:06,797
Where?

362
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:08,600
The Big Buddha Temple
on West Mountain.

363
00:16:10,887 --> 00:16:12,450
(Honor in the Martial World)

364
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,240
Chang.

365
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,840
Are you sure you don't need our help?

366
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,600
No need.

367
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:16,954
He's nothing but a brute.

368
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,441
Zhizhi and I can handle him.

369
00:16:20,425 --> 00:16:23,425
But I feel something's not right.

370
00:16:24,237 --> 00:16:25,237
What makes you say that?

371
00:16:25,415 --> 00:16:26,937
How did this thief, Liu San,

372
00:16:26,937 --> 00:16:28,456
just appear out of thin air?

373
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,250
And why set himself
against the Gate Bureau?

374
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,919
He's so mysterious that

375
00:16:32,031 --> 00:16:33,312
even the Beggar Sect and Wu Buzhi

376
00:16:33,312 --> 00:16:34,552
know nothing about him.

377
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:36,121
And then there's Liu Jun.

378
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,850
In just a single day,

379
00:16:37,850 --> 00:16:39,600
he found the hideout

380
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,439
that even the Gate Bureau couldn't find.

381
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,737
And it happens just as

382
00:16:43,737 --> 00:16:45,897
you decide to teach Liu San a lesson.

383
00:16:46,087 --> 00:16:47,487
You think it's a setup?

384
00:16:47,559 --> 00:16:48,399
But

385
00:16:48,759 --> 00:16:50,559
we've never crossed him.

386
00:16:51,639 --> 00:16:52,840
That may be true,

387
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:56,080
but it's all too much of a coincidence.

388
00:16:56,399 --> 00:16:57,279
I think

389
00:16:57,279 --> 00:16:58,280
we shouldn't

390
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,600
overthink this.

391
00:16:59,725 --> 00:17:00,565
Maybe

392
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:02,301
he's just some hotheaded fool

393
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:03,749
looking to make a name for himself.

394
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,440
We'll just give him a thrashing

395
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,119
and let the Gate Bureau deal with him.

396
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,279
I hope you're right.

397
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,119
I'm off.

398
00:17:13,737 --> 00:17:14,418
(Honor in the Martial World)
Wait.

399
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,400
Where is Zhizhi anyway?

400
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:17,360
Where did she go?

401
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:19,599
I'm meeting her on the outskirts.

402
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,240
Stay cautious.

403
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,400
Don't worry.

404
00:17:59,175 --> 00:18:02,450
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

405
00:18:02,488 --> 00:18:05,363
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

406
00:18:05,863 --> 00:18:11,581
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

407
00:18:12,763 --> 00:18:16,083
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

408
00:18:16,213 --> 00:18:19,133
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

409
00:18:20,301 --> 00:18:25,541
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

410
00:18:26,763 --> 00:18:29,156
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

411
00:18:29,156 --> 00:18:32,806
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

412
00:18:32,875 --> 00:18:36,365
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

413
00:18:36,463 --> 00:18:39,438
♪To the ends of time♪

414
00:18:39,438 --> 00:18:42,813
♪The moon traces your face♪

415
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:46,588
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

416
00:18:46,588 --> 00:18:52,828
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

417
00:18:53,163 --> 00:18:56,378
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

418
00:18:56,663 --> 00:19:00,201
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

419
00:19:00,488 --> 00:19:03,513
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

420
00:19:03,513 --> 00:19:06,613
♪On our way to forever♪

421
00:19:06,613 --> 00:19:10,463
♪The moon traces your face♪

422
00:19:10,463 --> 00:19:13,823
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

423
00:19:14,013 --> 00:19:19,973
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

424
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:30,690
♪Just to be with you♪
